sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as EPMS Web/Mobile UI
    participant BFF as Web BFF / Mobile BFF
    participant AIO as AI Orchestrator
    participant Auth as Azure AD / AuthZ
    participant MCP as MCP / Tool Adapter Layer
    participant Camp as Campaign Service
    participant WBS as WBS Service
    participant Rule as Rule Engine
    participant Search as Search Service
    participant LLM as LLM

    User->>UI: Ask: "Show all delayed WBS items for Campaign X"
    UI->>BFF: POST /api/ai/copilot/query
    Note over UI,BFF: Body: { query, channel, userContext }

    BFF->>Auth: Validate JWT / roles
    Auth-->>BFF: Token valid + user claims

    BFF->>AIO: POST /internal/ai/orchestrator/query
    Note over BFF,AIO: Body: { query, userId, roles, channel }

    AIO->>LLM: Interpret intent and entities
    Note over AIO,LLM: "Find delayed WBS items for campaign named Campaign X"
    LLM-->>AIO: intent=get_delayed_wbs_items,\ncampaignName=Campaign X,\nfilters={status: delayed}

    AIO->>MCP: POST /tools/campaigns/resolve
    Note over AIO,MCP: { campaignName: "Campaign X" }

    MCP->>Camp: GET /api/campaigns?name=Campaign%20X
    Camp-->>MCP: 200 OK [{campaignId, name, status}]
    MCP-->>AIO: campaignId=CMP-1024

    AIO->>MCP: POST /tools/access/check
    Note over AIO,MCP: { userId, resourceType: "Campaign", resourceId: "CMP-1024", action: "read" }

    MCP->>Auth: POST /internal/authorization/check
    Auth-->>MCP: allow
    MCP-->>AIO: accessGranted=true

    AIO->>MCP: POST /tools/wbs/search
    Note over AIO,MCP: { campaignId: "CMP-1024", delayedOnly: true }

    MCP->>WBS: GET /api/wbs-items?campaignId=CMP-1024&status=DELAYED
    WBS-->>MCP: 200 OK [wbs items]

    alt Delay must be derived, not stored
        MCP->>Rule: POST /api/rules/evaluate/wbs-delay
        Note over MCP,Rule: { campaignId, wbsItems, evaluationDate }
        Rule-->>MCP: delayed flags / computed delay reasons
    end

    opt Need enrichment for comments / latest updates
        MCP->>Search: GET /api/search?wbsIds=...&type=comment,status-update
        Search-->>MCP: related notes / latest updates
    end

    MCP-->>AIO: delayed WBS items + optional reasons/context

    AIO->>LLM: Format concise business response
    Note over AIO,LLM: Summarize list, counts, major blockers
    LLM-->>AIO: Final natural-language answer + table structure

    AIO-->>BFF: 200 OK {summary, items, totals}
    BFF-->>UI: 200 OK response payload
    UI-->>User: Show delayed WBS items for Campaign X